---
import "../../styles/style.css";
---
    <section class="h-screen w-screen p-4 px-10 text-[#27253D] bg-[#F6FFCA] flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-end items-center my-8 mx-12">
         <span class="flex flex-row space-between h-12 w-content gap-2 text-[16px] border border-[#2A014B] text-[#2A014B] items-center py-1 px-4 cursor-pointer">Star us on GitHub<img src="introgithub.png" /></span>
        </div>

    <div class="flex w-full flex-row space-between">
        <div class="w-2/6 flex flex-col gap-2 ml-6">
            <h1 class="serif text-[18px] text-[#2A014B] mb-1" >Introducing Solaris</h1>
                <p class="leading-7 text-[12px] text-[#2A014B] mb-2">Solaris is a platform for distributing a quantifiable amount of influence in a code base or project. These are referred to as credits. By assigning credits based on the quality and quantity of contributions, project maintainers can foster a collaborative environment where contributors feel valued and motivated to engage actively.</p>
            <h1 class="serif text-[18px] text-[#2A014B] mb-1" >Ownership</h1>
                <p class="leading-7 text-[12px] text-[#2A014B] mb-2">We are enabling maintainers to strategically distribute influence, ensuring that key stakeholders have the appropriate level of input in decision-making processes.</p>
            <h1 class="serif text-[18px] text-[#2A014B] mb-1" >Project Sustainability</h1>
            <p class="leading-7 text-[12px] text-[#2A014B] mb-2">Ultimately, customizable credit allocation promotes transparency, accountability, and efficiency in project management, driving the success and sustainability of open source initiatives.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="w-4/6 flex flex-row items-center justify-end">
            <img class="" src="solarisscreenshotmobile1.png" />
            <img class="" src="solarisscreenshot1.png" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-row justify-start items-center mx-6 w-full h-40">
    <div class="w-1/2">
         <div class="cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center gap-6 text-[#F6FFCA] bg-[#27253D] w-[174px] h-[44px]">
         <span class="text-[18px]">Try Solaris</span>
         <span><img src="externalintroducing.png" /></span>
         </div>
    </div>
       <span class="text-[#2A014B] flex flex-row items-start space-between underline">
    <span class="text-[22px] leading-10 w-2/3">Integrates with GitHub, Gitlab, and more to come.</span>
    <span class="flex w-1/3 flex-row items-end justify-end"><img src="githubintroducing.png" />
    <img src="gitlabintroducing.png" /></span>
    </span>
    </div>
</div>
</section>